1.10	Sam's_Town_Hotel_and_Gambling_Hall,_Tunica	Sam's Town Hotel and Gambling Hall, Tunica	The Tunica location of Sam's Town Hotel and Gambling Hall is located in Tunica Resorts, Mississippi. Officially known as a riverboat casino because the gaming area is situated on a building built on barges that float in a pool of water linked to the nearby Mississippi River as required by state law, the resort in all other aspects resembles its Nevada sibling, except for the atrium. It includes a 1,600 seat showroom, a 1,070-room hotel, and a RV park.	
